author: Channel Awesome
description:
It's another "Macho Man takes care of Kids" film, and what a shock it's awful. DisneyCember continues with a look at 2005's, The Pacifier.

Watch all DisneyCember here - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0AQIMR-tpomecW19RN2LNrdoqd5wFu4R

Watch the new NC - https://youtu.be/EkbsPkmj1hQ

The Pacifier is a 2005 American family action comedy film directed by Adam Shankman, written by Thomas Lennon and Robert Ben Garant and starring Vin Diesel. After a failed rescue mission, Navy SEAL Shane Wolfe is assigned as babysitter to the dead man's family.
